Citation.sTitle: Viscosity of [bmim][PF6] and [bmim][BF4] at High Pressure
Citation.sAbstract: The viscosities of 1-butyl-3-methylimidazolium hexafluorophosphate ([bmim] [PF6]) and 1-butyl-3-methylimidazolium tetrafluoroborate ([bmim][BF4]) were measured by using a rolling-ball viscometer. The experimental temperatures were from 293.15 to 353.15 K, and the pressures were from 0.1 to 20.0MPa.
